Calibration Curves obtained from H2ag11sc.dat at 2E13 cm[-2]

   Calibrated spectra filename: H2ag11sc.cal
   Sensitivity filename         H2euv_sen.txt


Calibration was done in 2 regions, from 814 to 990 A and from
920 to 1445 A.  The values listed belowed are a merger of the
sensitivty curves obtained in the 2 regions. The merge is performed
in region 915-950 A.

The error of calibration in region 810-920 can be as large as 25-30%
due to poor S/N ratio and blending of higher (B", D' & D" etc) Rydberg
states, whose the transition probabilities are not available. The
calibration error between 930 and 1400 region should be less than
10-15%

